author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Electrical box location tips…I need to add a single gang box for my LED shower niche switch. I need to factor in the tile floor thickness. In this situation it’ll be roughly 1 inch thick due to self-leveler, DITRA, thin-set, and the tile. So I made the top of the box at about 49 inches off the floor because in the end it’ll be closer to 48 inches which is what code recommends 🔥#electrical #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
title: Electrical Box Location Tip - #shorts #electrical #homerepairtutor
